--- Lynxiz ---

Lynxiz sprints away from the fighting, carrying Trinity all the while,  
trying to get behind the mountain closest to the Chivitron base. "I've 
got to keep you safe little one..." She says soothingly to the tiny 
bot in stasis lock. She tries to cover some of the child's wounds as 
she runs.
